},{"pid":"73440f742bbe0c67ec9c0c989e6539c99814a41c","tid":458943,"uid":118480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T11:28:22.000Z","msg":"出水學姐榨汁姬 is the best<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不接受任何反駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846bbce7bd0ed15dad641f56d2766e97e78e0576","tid":458943,"uid":62068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T11:29:42.000Z","msg":"支持。"},{"pid":"34b17b99ddc669d5c99b8430448878757c93a080","tid":458943,"uid":7336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:04:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係玩過日向線</blockquote><br />\n星音線都值得玩吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定巴打都我都係同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2060d8419edf30956b1e777cfcb2b164c8669dec","tid":458943,"uid":7336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:04:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>難得有人打長文講galgame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我第一隻GalGame嚟，見幾啱我心水就想推廣吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到巴打你都有打文，你都好勁啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有興趣既過黎gal post交流下</blockquote><br />\n得閒會睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0bb311ae952410682769371de83d1a5a9a9f2e1","tid":458943,"uid":7336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:07:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出水學姐榨汁姬 is the best<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不接受任何反駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知點解我覺得星音比出水學姐更加似榨汁姬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca561b4577109d